DESCRIPTION:Provider: SpaceX\nLaunch site: Cape Canaveral SFS\, FL\, USA\n
 \nThe Globalstar global mobile communications network offers global\, digi
 tal real time voice\, data and fax services via its Low Earth Orbit satell
 ite constellation. The constellation operates in a 1410 km orbit inclined 
 at 52 degrees.\n\nIn early 2022\, Globalstar contracted with MDA for the c
 onstruction of 17 new 2nd generation refresh satellites to replenish the e
 xisting constellation. Rocket Lab is sub-contracted to build the satellite
 s' buses and the launch dispensers.\n\nDetails: https://ll.thespacedevs.co
 m/2.3.0/launches/be8b4b0d-1989-48a5-a96d-e8e4d59ed8b3/?format=json
LOCATION:Cape Canaveral SFS\, FL\, USA
