DESCRIPTION:Provider: SpaceX\nLaunch site: Cape Canaveral SFS\, FL\, USA\n
 \nSpaceX Crew-13 is the thirteenth crewed operational flight of a Crew Dra
 gon spacecraft to the International Space Station as part of NASA's Commer
 cial Crew Program.\n\nDetails: https://ll.thespacedevs.com/2.3.0/launches/
 18441371-8b2e-457c-afb5-1ec1b11ab630/?format=json
LOCATION:Cape Canaveral SFS\, FL\, USA
